The manga version by Ippei Kuri was serialized in {{nihongo|''[[Adventure King]]''|冒険王|Bouken Ou}} magazine,<ref>{{cite book|title=超人画報―国産架空ヒーロー四十年の歩み (Chōjin Gahō Kokusan Kakū Hīrō Yon Jū-nen no Ayumi)|date=November 30, 1995|publisher=株式会社竹書房 (Takeshobo Co.Ltd.)|location=Japan|isbn=4-88475-874-9|page=45}}</ref> and the [[tankōbon]] was published in 2010.

